document_data.caption: A map showing Corwell Firth off the coast of Gwynneth.
document_data.name: Corwell Firth
document_data.mainbody: '''Corwell Firth''' was an inlet of the [[Trackless Sea]] located off the island of [[Gwynneth]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles}}
document_data.Geography: Corwell Firth formed a large natural harbor for the southeastern region of Gwynneth. The inlet measured roughly {{SI|50|mi|k|long=yes}} from its beginning near the [[Meirig Peatlands]] to its end at [[Caer Corwell]].
